summary: AN ORDINANCE relating to the Water Department authorizing the sale and conveyance by Quit Claim Deed of portion of a real property commonly known as the Lake Youngs Aqueduct Right-of Way (LYA R/W) located in Section 22, Township 22 North, Range 6 East W.M. King County, Washington, to Cecil R. and Sherry A. Grant, husband and wife.
